flowchart LR
    CONV[conversation] --> FILT[strip tool noise +<br/>ephemeral file paths]
    FILT --> Q[debounced queue<br/>~30s, batched]
    Q --> EX[LLM fact extraction<br/>+ confidence score]
    EX --> GATE{confidence ≥ 0.7?}
    GATE -->|yes| STORE[(memory.json + index)]
    GATE -->|no| DROP[discard]
